Package pl.polsl.model

package pl.polsl.model
The `pl.polsl.model` package includes classes representing the model component of the application, handling data structures, business logic, and database interactions.
Version:
3.0
Author:
Pawel Drzazga
  • Class
    Description
    AdminUser
    Represents an admin user in the application.

    TableModel class extends AbstractTableModel to provide a custom table model for Swing JTable.
